@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.abs(((v0 + 0.40 + v2 + 0.39) / v0))
    v2 = (tmp - 0.27)
    tmp = wp.cos(wp.sin(wp.cos(tmp + 0.94)))
    v0 = wp.abs(((v1 + 0.93 * tmp + 0.12) - 0.96))
    v0 = wp.cos(v1)
    v0 = (wp.exp(wp.abs(tmp + 0.11)) * (0.07 / v2))
    v0 = (wp.cos(0.75) + (wp.exp(v2 + 0.33) - (tmp + 0.28 - v2 + 0.45)))
    data[tid] = v0
